    "name": "Mercure Kuta Bali",
    "detail": "When we arrivved at the mercure hotel it was the second time i have been there & chose the same hotel after great service fromthe hotel. The hotel has a great eternity pool over looking the sea & beach & love to hang out there in the midday sun most days & at night close to so many food choices. Other things are the friendly, relaiable staff who are very welcoming & understand a customers needs. My wife & i love this hotel & will reccomend this hotel to anyone wishing a great time in bali in a safe enviroment in relaxing, fun area, mercure is myfav hotel in bali & will come back many times more :)",
