  {
    "hotel_id": "633617",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/astagina-resort-villa-and-spa/hotel/bali-id.html",
    "name": "Astagina Resort Villa and Spa",
    "detail": "Me and my friend booked for 2 nights in Astagina and another 1 night on our last day in Bali. Staffs were very hospitable especially the ones in the conceirge - Krisna, Sinta, and Bayu - they were very attentive to our requests and helped us in everyway possible to make our vacation wonderful. Upon check-in, we already informed them that we will be having our tour the next day thus we cannot go to the breakfast but they can give us “breakfast box” instead, aggreed and set the delivery of the said box at 5-5:30am. Next day came, hoping for something “big” for the breakfast box but we received a box of 3 types of bread, 2 kinds of fruits, some jam and butter, and a bottle of water each. We didn’t complain thinking maybe it is what is served for breakfast in the hotel, and it is still early that time. On our last day, we went to join in for breakfast where we witness how different the servings from what we received the other morning, there were many varieties to choose from. Then we had another booking to the same hotel after 2 days, wherein we now checked-in in a twin beds room, room is spacious. Anyhow, our overall stay were wonderful that is why we still booked another night on our last day in Bali, and planning to stay in the same hotel when we go back to Bali.",
